TestWhereOnApexErrors
/ 5 where age > 20 — meaningless on a scalar, errors clearly. where lives only on
/ field-bearing types (dict, and list via its elements), never the apex.
- set %x% = 5
- where %x% age > 20, on error key="WhereOnApex" write out "rejected as expected", write to %r%
- assert %r% equals "rejected as expected"
